          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ", destined) ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "to see",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". Elisha partly imitates the speech of the scoffer, which begins in the Hebrew with “Behold, Jehovah is about to make windows.” (Comp. ",
