        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; etc. The term itself, שׁלישׁ  shâlı̂ysh (derived from שׁלושׁ  shâlôsh, \"three,\") may be compared with the Latin \"tribunus.\"",
        "children": []
