        "text": "Windows - Rather, \"sluices\" (compare Genesis 7:11). The \"lord\" means to say \"If Yahweh were to open sluices in heaven, and pour down grain as He poured down rain in the time of the Deluge, even then could there be such abudnance as thou speakest of?\" ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
